      <list id="id233068" display="block" list-type="enumerated">
        <item id="uid14">Plot a graph of pressure (p) against volume (V). Volume will be on the x-axis and pressure on the y-axis. Describe the relationship that you see.
</item>
        <item id="uid15">Plot a graph of <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> against <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Describe the relationship that you see.
